data.text:
Watch West Ham United live all season long in New York City. The NYC Hammers have been going strong for over a decade now, cheering on the Hammers come rain or shine. Smithfield Hall is open for every available West Ham United game.

THE NYC Hammers

Facebook: NewYorkCityHammers

Twitter: nychammers

Check EPL fixtures at: smithfieldnyc.com/football/england

Official MUFC website: www.whufc.com

BPL table: www.premierleague.com

Smithfield is proud to have The NYC Hammers as one of our supporters clubs and encourage all fans of West Ham United to join them. Smithfield, the best place to watch West Ham United in New York.
